data.description: This beautiful home sits at the end of a culdesac and features formal living, formal dining, a huge great room, and a large kitchen. The entire first floor has really nice 18x18 tile flooring. The kitchen features Dark cabinets and granite counters and opens up to the huge great room, which features a nice built in entertainment center. The second floor has wood floors in the hallway and at the office niche and carpet in the bedrooms. The laundry room is upstairs for convenience. The front load washer and dryer will stay if you want them to. Very nice home with a great floor plan and nice 3 car garage.
